data.description: Fully Remodeled and Fully Furnished short term rental / Mid term rental investment in the heart of NW Atlanta. This Turnkey 4 bedroom 3 bath was thoughtfully furnished/decorated by an interior designer to stand out and attract guests to this home.      KEY FEATURES     **Exterior: Freshly painted with a custom concrete staircase and a cozy front porch.  **Interior: Open living area with white/grey tones, and an accent wall, leading to a stylish kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances and a view of the front yard.  **Bedrooms: Three main level bedrooms, including a master suite with a spa-like shower, plus an additional bedroom, bath, living room, and office nook in the finished basement.  **Outdoor & Location: Includes a carport, backyard access with a concrete deck, and close proximity to Atlanta's top attractions (i.e. Six Flags, Airport, and Downtown) This home is not only perfect for those seeking a turnkey city dwelling but also offers an excellent short-term rental opportunity, fully furnished and ready for the summer season in metro Atlanta.  **Turnkey Investment Opportunity: Fully furnished active Short Term Rental heading into the peak summer months. Seller will provide the photos from listing to buyer if requested.    Whether you are looking to purchase a home for you and the family or are looking for a turnkey fully furnished rental, this home is for you!
